{"TopicId":204014,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"KSP 2 Ideas that don\u0026#039;t merit their own thread.","CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-25T23:01:14Z","PageNum":3,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T02:05:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043104\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634257117\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216191\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Synonym Toast Crunch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Synonym Toast Crunch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAirbag landings like the Mars Pathfinder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh yes, practical lithobraking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like that. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-15T02:05:13Z\u0022 title=\u002210/15/2021 02:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 15, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Admiral Fluffy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eoh hey llok new page\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T12:58:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAn add-on for \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Solid fuel Rocket Booster\u0022\u003ESRB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u0027s that let them gimbal using LOX.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SOXBLOX","CreatedById":204106,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-15T20:34:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was thinking about camera angles and stuff...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf there are going to be cameras as science parts or something, then could we set them as our viewpoint? That way we could see exactly what Mission Control would see. I think it might be a nice touch...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hyperspace Industries","CreatedById":212417,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-16T11:31:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHotkeys for retrograde, prograde, and other \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003Esas\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA way to record in game videos, without the ui showing on them, but with the ui visible to you while you play.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-16T14:46:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043607\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634383898\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212417\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hyperspace Industries\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Hyperspace Industries said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA way to record in game videos, without the ui showing on them, but with the ui visible to you while you play\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYES\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheOrbitalMechanic","CreatedById":216179,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-18T22:18:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps a \u0022heat shield\u0022 paint color, so you can add custom heat shields to craft with the paint editor? It would add weight and cost, and potentially require ablator, but I think the potential of more heat-resistant spaceplanes would be worth it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TLTay","CreatedById":184633,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T20:59:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould we get a landing radar part for use when landing in the dark? It could display the ground in a low fidelity green phosphor grid pattern or something on screen so we have some idea where we are in relation to the features around us. Bonus points for short range and conical fov.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T21:12:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634849977\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184633\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TLTay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, TLTay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould we get a landing radar part for use when landing in the dark? It could display the ground in a low fidelity green phosphor grid pattern or something on screen so we have some idea where we are in relation to the features around us. Bonus points for short range and conical fov.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat would be really nice, but not for initial release, because there is an easy workaround: Lights\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheOrbitalMechanic","CreatedById":216179,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-21T22:14:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224045690\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634849977\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184633\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TLTay\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, TLTay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCould we get a landing radar part for use when landing in the dark? It could display the ground in a low fidelity green phosphor grid pattern or something on screen so we have some idea where we are in relation to the features around us. Bonus points for short range and conical fov.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould also be useful for IVA-only missions! I like this idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kenny Kerman","CreatedById":175645,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-29T15:19:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA smoke canister to make visual land markers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReal small parachutes, to drop little things (like smoke canisters... \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E )\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLabels for the surface lights... So you can make a board to see the state of the parts controlled by actions groups.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA gyroscope to have data about the angles around the vertical, to make autopilots easy to build, and copters easy to pilot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd a Dr Who electric screwdriver.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-10-29T15:25:15Z\u0022 title=\u002210/29/2021 03:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 29, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Kenny Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Emore ideas\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"shdwlrd","CreatedById":113880,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-29T18:23:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCredit goes to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/211250-the-doodling-astronaut/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022211250\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/211250-the-doodling-astronaut/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@The Doodling Astronaut\u003C/a\u003Efor this. But the kerbals surnames are based on what planets or \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E the colony is based on/in. So if the colony is based on Dres, the kerbals from there would have the surname of Dresmen.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-29T18:24:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224048700\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221635531816\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022113880\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022shdwlrd\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, shdwlrd said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDres\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WhatALovelyNick","CreatedById":216611,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-31T20:16:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMirrors, just... mirrors!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Staticalliam7","CreatedById":216180,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-10-31T23:22:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043607\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634383898\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212417\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Hyperspace Industries\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/16/2021 at 7:31 AM, Hyperspace Industries said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA way to record in game videos, without the ui showing on them, but with the ui visible to you while you play.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeconded!\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheOrbitalMechanic","CreatedById":216179,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-08T01:15:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about the ability for Kerbals to stand on the exterior of ships that are under thrust? Currently they just kinda flop around when not on a ladder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-09T16:53:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224043123\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634263504\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210816\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Admiral Fluffy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/15/2021 at 4:05 AM, Admiral Fluffy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh yes, practical lithobraking.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really like that. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemember having an\u00A0Pathfinder mod back before we had stock rovers. It was very easy to land because of the air bags. I even used it to land on airless bodies with an top mounted stage, it was often not needed to remove it after litobreaking \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0as I was not very good at landing back then.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LHACK4142","CreatedById":208897,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-10T00:49:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want KSP2\u0027s music to reference KSP1\u0027s music. Age of Empires IV does that with AoE 2\u0027s, and very well in my opinion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tremonthedgehog","CreatedById":217052,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-19T23:55:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbuilt in mod ui?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tremonthedgehog","CreatedById":217052,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-19T23:56:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlike you can install mods without using file explorer kinda like steam\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSameKerbal77","CreatedById":217455,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-20T17:47:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224012887\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221627760140\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022182413\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Bej Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/31/2021 at 1:35 PM, Bej Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt doesn\u0027t matter, orbital decay would only serve as a distraction from actual gameplay. You will have unstable orbits in proximity to Rask and Rusk to look forward to though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSounds like work for the modders!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224044524\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221634595502\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216179\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheOrbitalMechanic\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/18/2021 at 4:18 PM, TheOrbitalMechanic said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps a \u0022heat shield\u0022 paint color, so you can add custom heat shields to craft with the paint editor? It would add weight and cost, and potentially require ablator, but I think the potential of more heat-resistant spaceplanes would be worth it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you mean heat shield paint? So say your land legs burn up on reentry but nothing else we could add heat resistance paint to add maybe 15%, 10% whatever the devs find balanced. Could of course be a mod though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-20T21:02:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224057582\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204014\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221637430471\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217455\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheSameKerbal77\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, TheSameKerbal77 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you mean heat shield paint?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother thing would be tiles, like on the Shuttle.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Staticalliam7","CreatedById":216180,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-20T22:52:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nheat shield tiles that dynamically wrap around the bottom of a space craft - would make shuttle tiles easier\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwouldn\u0027t really be that hard to implement either\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-21T07:18:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u002B1\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd the heat shield tiles as parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ZlBSm.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022125.00\u0022 height=\u0022800\u0022 width=\u0022640\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.stack.imgur.com/ZlBSm.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tremonthedgehog","CreatedById":217052,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-21T17:03:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthat\u0027s a good idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Staticalliam7","CreatedById":216180,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-26T07:25:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how to explain this idea, but gravioli \u0026gt; ravioli\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}